HEADWORD: extraterrestrial
<hw>ex`tra*ter*res"tri*al</hw>
<pr>(⟦ecr⟧ks`tr⟦adot⟧*t⟦ecr⟧r`r⟦ecr⟧s"tr⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>adj.</pos> <def>originating or located or occurring outside Earth
or its atmosphere; <as>as, there is no clear evidence for
<ex>extraterrestrial</ex> life</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

